 These students prove it by singing a Japanese song they learned last year.
<time sec="696.342"/>
 [[NS]]
<time sec="698.799"/>
 Scientists say they still don't know when is the best time to learn a second language.
<time sec="702.786"/>
 They eventually hope to answer that question, by more study on how the brain learns language.
<time sec="708.130"/>
 Ann Kellan, CNN reporting.
</turn>
